# Project documentation

- **Single source of truth**: All product, setup, and implementation details live in **specs.md** at the project root.
- When you implement or change a feature, **update specs.md** accordingly (new sections, revised steps, new migrations, env vars, etc.).
- **Do not** create separate markdown files per feature or implementation (e.g. no `FEATURE_NAME.md`, `SETUP_WEB.md`). Keep everything in specs.md.
